{"version":1,"entries":{"person_1675379_translations":{"at":1772653597266,"data":{"id":1675379,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"　　张皓然，1983年2月9日出生于河北省邯郸市 ，中国内地男演员，曾经在驻港部队服役，退役后考入中央戏剧学院。身高：181cm 体重73kg。2015年因在古装传奇励志剧《女医·明妃传》中饰演太医院弟子程村霞而为观众所熟识。出演电影《笔仙2》、《张震讲故事》；外形硬朗的他在2019年出演警匪动作电影《“大”人物》，主演动作剧《瞄准》和科幻悬疑剧《在劫难逃》；2021年出演电视剧《扫黑风暴》。","name":"张皓然","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Zhang Haoran","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"張皓然","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"張皓然，1983 年 2 月 9 日出生於河北省邯鄲市 ，中國內地男演員，曾經在駐港部隊服役，退役後考入中央戲劇學院。身高：181cm 體重 73kg。2015 年因在古裝傳奇勵志劇《女醫·明妃傳》中飾演太醫院弟子程村霞而為觀眾所熟識。出演電影《筆仙 2》、《張震講故事》；外形硬朗的他在 2019 年出演警匪動作電影《“大”人物》，主演動作劇《瞄準》和科幻懸疑劇《在劫難逃》；2021 年出演電視劇《掃黑風暴》。","name":"張皓然","primary":false}}]}},"person_53936_translations":{"at":1772653602256,"data":{"id":53936,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia\n\nMelonie Díaz (born April 25, 1984) is an American actress who has been appeared in many independent films, including four shown at the 2008 Sundance Film Festival.\n\nDescription above from the Wikipedia article Melonie Díaz , licensed under CC-BY-SA, full list of contributors on Wikipedia.","name":"Melonie Díaz","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"梅洛妮·迪亚兹（Melonie Diaz，1984 年 4 月 25 日出生）是一位美国女演员","name":"梅洛妮·迪亚兹","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"ES","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"bio